title: Plat 1 mid/jgl LF team or duo
body:
http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=Meenks


Would love to find a competitive team to play with, my goal this season is to reach master / challenger, and will keep improving until I reach it. I have alot of spare time, and would be able to travel and even relocate if I find a team.

Feel free to add me ingame for a chat, am looking for teams / players around and above diamond.
